{
  "stem": "5559.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the soup was made what they call a potato soup-- but these little-- with sand and, you know, and stones from the farm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they don't sell that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the chicken pick it up on the farm, and the pigs-- that was the soup.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if you were dumb enough-- of course, hungry enough you were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's no question-- but if you were stupid enough to figure that that will help you survive, and you eat it or drink, in two days, you were dead in the latrine, thrown in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a trench, what's called latrine, with everything in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that is your burial place with everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have to take it and throw in the latrine, because you got, right away, dysentery and everything-- poison.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just it was maybe two days a slower death then you take green poison, it maybe takes 10 minutes if there is, or you see Dr.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Kevorkian, and he can do a better job on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us over the river, over the water, in a-- in a very low boat-- low boat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, if you picked up-- and I'd like to mention, if you ever picked up a ration, a can, what the Germans used to have maybe butter in there also, and if they saw you, they kill you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't want you to have any kind of utensil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you were lucky enough, [INAUDIBLE] you got it, then you go in the water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, you have about-- that water, and some little fish are swimming in-- into the-- into the can.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it seems like these little fish also with that water did not infect you with any-- it seems.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
